data.description: Fall in Love with this ALL Brick 2 Story Home with Tons of Character! Enter into the large Living Room with beautiful built-in shelves and a brick fireplace that adds so much charm! The Kitchen features include a center island and ample cabinet space. Head upstairs to check out the extremely spacious Main Bedroom, along with two additional Bedrooms and Full Bath.  The downstairs Rec Room can be used for relaxation, entertainment, and more! Venture out back to the large fenced in yard with a beautiful patio space for lounging outdoors or entertaining guests. This home has so much to offer! You won't want to miss it! Schedule your tour today!
